# {FlavorFinder}
#### {Recipe Discovery Platform}, {April 20, 2025}
#### By **{Adriel Macharia}**

## Description
{FlavorFinder is a community-driven recipe platform that helps home cooks discover, save, and share delicious meals with features like AI-powered search, dietary filters, and interactive cooking mode.}

## Setup/Installation Requirements
* Clone repository: git clone https://github.com/AdrielMacharia/FlavorFinder.git
* Install dependencies: npm install
* Configure environment variables
* Start the app: npm run dev

## Known Bugs
* Image upload fails in Safari
* Metric conversion rounding errors
* Mobile menu sometimes sticks

## Technologies Used
* Frontend: React, Tailwind CSS
* Backend: Node.js, Express
* Database: MongoDB
* APIs: Spoonacular, Firebase

## Support and contact details
* Email: adriel@example.com
* GitHub Issues: https://github.com/AdrielMacharia/FlavorFinder/issues

